BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[FFXIV] Moogle Treasure Trove – The Hunt for Aphorism Commences 
 March 31!
DTSTART:20260324T080000Z
DTEND:20260407T080000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T064504Z
UID:26c7f3e73070@mmo-calendar
DESCRIPTION:It gives us great pleasure to announce the return of the Moogl
 e Treasure Trove starting Tuesday\, March 31\, 2026!\n\nCollect irregular 
 tomestones of aphorism by completing specific duties and exchange them wit
 h itinerant moogles for a host of treasures including accessories and moun
 ts. Seek out those tomestones and reap the rewards!\n\nNew to these exclus
 ive offerings is the miner's earring. Chip away at challenges and boast th
 e proof of your labors!\n\nVisit the Moogle Treasure Trove – The Hunt fo
 r Aphorism special site.\n\n\n* Irregular tomestones of aphorism will not 
 be awarded when using adventurer squadrons or the Duty Support system. \n*
  Unrestricted parties must have the "Level Sync" option enabled to receive
  irregular tomestones of aphorism.
URL:https://na.finalfantasyxiv.com/lodestone/topics/detail/7a0edfe3976b1a7
 9e7daac093c191fed3aaf9b8f
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[FFXIV] Hatching-tide Begins March 23!
DTSTART:20260323T000000Z
DTEND:20260406T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260410T064506Z
UID:e8497ec37fb0@mmo-calendar
DESCRIPTION:Spring has sprung\, and across the realm\, festivities unfold 
 in celebration of profoundly prophetic dreams and exceptionally eggy eggs.
  A stylish Dreamer awaits the aid of an adventurer keen to fight\, seek\, 
 and reap the rewards of this vibrant season!\n\n Read on for details.
URL:https://na.finalfantasyxiv.com/lodestone/topics/detail/187a47be0828ae3
 00b720e9200421045bd32efd0
END:VEVENT
